abstract: >
  Open-source infrastructure and reference implementation for Argentine
  sociedades-IA (AI-only companies) under the regime announced by the
  Ministry of Desregulación on 28 April 2026. The package comprises 17
  Vercel-AI-SDK-compatible npm libraries spanning MercadoPago, AFIP/ARCA
  identity + factura electrónica, WhatsApp Business, banking, shipping,
  GDE/TAD, BCRA, IGJ, Boletín Oficial, and MercadoLibre integration; 26
  cookbook recipes; four RFCs (001-004) covering civil liability,
  agent discovery, cross-jurisdictional reciprocity, and the normative
  operational-log wire format; seven frozen conformance test vectors;
  a public certifier that scores any URL 0-100 against RFC-002 + RFC-004
  in seconds; a reference implementation that self-certifies at 100/100.
